  "text": "Premature expression of Hec1/Cdh Fzr blocks mitotic cycles and induces premature endocycles ( Fig. 2A-E) . Lack of string at stage 4-6 shows similar phenotypes [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . We therefore analyzed whether overproduction of Hec1/Cdh Fzr caused a premature repression of String levels. However, no effect on string (or dacapo) expression was observed in cells that prematurely expressed fzr and entered endocycles (Fig. 6C,D) .",
